st%20Contest%20In%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnda%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP's%20ruling%20coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Congress'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2FINDIA-alliance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EINDIA%20opposition%20bloc%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20go%20head-to-head%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20battle%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker's%20post%20-%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20in%20a%20parliamentary%20democracy%20and%20to%20be%20held%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20decades%20-%20after%20the%20two%20failed%20to%20agree%20a%20division%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20and%20his%2Fher%20deputy%20-%20the%20post%20fuelling%20disagreements%20between%20the%20two%20political%20giants%20-%20are%20usually%20elected%20by%20consensus%2C%20lack%20of%20which%20in%20this%20instance%20underlines%20the%20fractious%20BJP-Congress%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20-%20scheduled%20for%2011%20am%20tomorrow%20-%20will%20see%20the%20BJP's%20Om%20Birla%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%20from%20Kota%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20up%20against%20the%20Congress'%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%2C%20an%20eight-term%20parliamentarian%20from%20Kerala's%20Mavelikara.%20Mr%20Suresh%20is%20the%20longest-serving%20parliamentarian%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla%20is%20likely%20to%20win%20given%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance's%20majority%3B%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20is%20elected%20by%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20MPs%20voting%20and%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20can%20call%20on%20293%20votes%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20232.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20filing%20his%20papers%20Mr%20Suresh%20told%20the%20press%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20party's%20decision...%20not%20mine.%20There%20is%20a%20convention...%20that%20Deputy%20Speaker%20will%20be%20from%20the%20opposition.%20But%20they%20(the%20BJP)%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20do%20this.%20We%20were%20waiting%20till%2011.50%20am...%20but%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20So%20we%20filed%20the%20nomination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20however%2C%20countered%20that%20claim%2C%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20precedent%20to%20suggest%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker's%20post%20must%20go%20to%20a%20member%20of%20an%20opposition%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Seeks%20Consensus%2C%20Congress%20Replies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20much%20drama%20this%20morning%20-%20ahead%20of%20the%20noon%20deadline%20to%20file%20nominations%20-%20as%20the%20BJP%20sought%20the%20opposition's%20consensus%20over%20the%20re-appointment%20of%20Mr%20Birla%20as%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20were%20so%20tasked.%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20Mr%20Rijiju%20met%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20Congress'%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20were%20told%20consensus%20relied%20on%20the%20opposition%20getting%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-speaker-election-government-reaches-out-to-india-for-consensus-over-speaker-sources-5963962%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Speaker%20Row%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20Call%2C%20Congress'%20Deputy%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy's%20chair%20is%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20an%20opposition%20MP%20to%20ensure%20a%20balanced%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20was%20not%20filled%20in%20the%20second%20Modi%20government%20(2019-2024)%2C%20but%20in%20the%20first%20(2014-2019)%2C%20it%20was%20awarded%20to%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20-%20the%20AIADMK's%20M%20Thambidurai%20held%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20meeting%20with%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20did%20not%20go%20as%20hoped%3B%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20said%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20support%20Mr%20Birla's%20candidate%20providing%20it%20was%20given%20the%20deputy's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20BJP%20was%20not%20forthcoming%20on%20this%20demand%3B%20the%20party%20reportedly%20wanted%20immediate%20consensus%20for%20Mr%20Birla%20and%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20his%20deputy%20would%20be%20taken%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-amid-government-opposition-talks-on-speaker-om-birlas-meet-with-pm-5964367%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOm%20Birla%20To%20Be%20Speaker%20Again%2C%20BJP-Led%20Govt%20Sticks%20To%20Continuity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20play%20ball%20and%2C%20as%20the%20clock%20ticked%20down%20to%20the%20noon%20deadline%2C%20whispers%20emerged%20that%20the%20Congress'%20K%20Suresh%20would%20be%20offered%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20it%20happened%3B%20as%20visuals%20showed%20senior%20leaders%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20accompanying%20Mr%20Birla%20to%20file%20his%20papers%2C%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20Mr%20Suresh%20had%20submitted%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20inevitable%20back-and-forth%20to%20follow%2C%20BJP%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20efforts%20had%20been%20made%20to%20build%20consensus%20with%20an%20opposition%20that%20responded%20with%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Congress'%20KC%20Venugopal%20and%20TR%20Baalu%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20DMK%20insisted%20on%20a%20commitment%20from%20the%20BJP%20-%20one%20to%20the%20effect%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20would%20be%20an%20opposition%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20sources%20-%20who%20also%20said%20the%20BJP%20had%20indicated%20its%20unwillingness%20to%20offer%20such%20an%20assurance%20-%20blamed%20the%20opposition's%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20commitment%20led%20to%20a%20failure%20of%20consensus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrinamool%20Twist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20a%20plot%20twist%20brewing%20backstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20-%20on%20paper%20a%20part%20of%20INDIA%20-%20was%20not%20consulted%20in%20nominating%20Mr%20Suresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20how%20to%20react%20by%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party%20has%20a%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20the%20Congress-led%20opposition%20grouping%3B%20there%20remains%20a%20perennial%20'will%20she%2C%20won't%20she'%20question%20mark%20over%20her%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20while%20the%20general%20election%20was%20on%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20offered%20her%20backing%2C%20telling%20reporters%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20She%20even%20called%20the%20opposition%20group%20her%20%26quot%3Bbrainchild%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-mamata-banerjee-india-alliance-i-dont-trust-mamata-banerjee-congress-adhir-ranjan-on-india-olive-branch-5677385%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPart%20Of%20INDIA%26quot%3B%20Says%20Mamata.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Trust%2C%26quot%3B%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Responds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%20Ms%20Banerjee%20-%20who%20had%20put%20her%20membership%20of%20the%20bloc%20on%20hold%20after%20public%20spats%20over%20seat-sharing%20deals%20-%20declared%20she%20would%20provide%20%26quot%3Boutside%20support%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20e