rial%20to%20protest%20against%20press%20censorship%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20proclamation%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20devised%20a%2020-point%20economic%20programme.%20Alongside%20began%20a%20brutal%20crackdown%20against%20the%20Opposition.%20Reports%20claim%20the%20excesses%20were%20engineered%20by%20a%20control%20group%20comprising%20loyalists%20of%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20and%20led%20by%20her%20younger%20Sanjay%20Gandhi.%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20held%20no%20Constitutional%20post%20at%20the%20point%2C%20came%20up%20with%20his%20own%20five-point%20agenda%20for%20literacy%2C%20family%20planning%2C%20tree%20planting%2C%20eradication%20of%20casteism%20and%20abolition%20of%20dowry.%20These%20initiatives%2C%20especially%20the%20family%20planning%20move%2C%20led%20to%20massive%20excesses%20such%20as%20forced%20mass%20sterilisation.%20Censorship%20was%20imposed%20and%20any%20news%20report%20against%20the%20government%20attracted%20consequences.%20Stooges%20of%20the%20government%20cleared%20newspapers%20before%20publication.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20when%20The%20Indian%20Express%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20to%20register%20its%20protest%20against%20censorship.%20The%20unsuspecting%20censor%20missed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Kuldip%20Nayar%2C%20in%20his%20book%20Emergency%20Retold%2C%20cited%20another%20example.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Statesman%20published%20a%20photograph%20by%20the%20gifted%20photographer%20Raghu%20Rai%20that%20told%20all%3A%20it%20showed%20a%20man%20peddling%20a%20cycle%20with%20two%20children%20on%20it%2C%20a%20woman%20walking%20behind%2C%20and%20scores%20of%20policemen%20standing%20all%20around.%20The%20caption%20said%20that%20life%20was%20normal%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk.%20A%20censor%20official%2C%20without%20realising%20the%20message%20the%20photo%20conveyed%2C%20'passed'%20it%20and%20was%20transferred%20the%20very%20next%20