%2C%20who%20once%20affectionately%20called%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20'Indu'%20and%20backed%20her%20wholeheartedly%20as%20she%20took%20on%20the%20Congress%20old%20guard%20after%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20verdict%2C%20JP%2C%20as%20he%20was%20popularly%20called%2C%20was%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20In%20a%20massive%20rally%20in%20Patna's%20Ramlila%20Maidan%2C%20JP%20recited%20Ramdhari%20Singh%20Dinkar's%20iconic%20lines%20that%20became%20a%20battle%20cry%20against%20Mrs%20Gandhi's%20dispensation%3A%20%26quot%3Bsinghasan%20khali%20karo%20ke%20janta%20aati%20hai%26quot%3B%20(vacate%20the%20throne%2C%20the%20people%20are%20coming).%20Soon%20after%20the%20Emergency%20was%20imposed%2C%20JP%20was%20arrested.%20A%20diabetic%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20fast%20unto%20death.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20which%20he%20sarcastically%20called%20her%20Mr%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20not%20'Indu'.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20watched%20with%20dismay%20and%20growing%20agony%20the%20way%20you%20have%20been%20pushing%20down%20the%20country%20ever%20deeper%20into%20the%20abyss%20of%20darkness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20released%20on%20November%2012%2C%201975%2C%20but%20the%20detention%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20health%20that%20he%20won't%20fully%20recover%20from%20till%20his%20death%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20JP%2C%20leaders%20of%20all%20political%20ideologies%20and%20hues%20came%20together%20to%20take%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi.%20It%20was%20under%20his%20guidance%20that%20the%20Janata%20Party%20was%20formed%20that%20would%20later%20crush%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%201977%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Big%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Constitutional%20rights%20suspended%20due%20to%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20used%20the%20Congress's%20majority%20in%20parliament%20to%20delay%20the%201976%20elections.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20the%20polls.%20While%20this%20surprise%20decision%20is%20often%20linked%20to%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20inputs%20that%20she%20was%20set%20to%20sweep%20the%20polls%2C%20some%20accounts%20claimed%20that%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20told%20her%20aides%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20lose...%20however%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%20for%20me%20to%20call%20for%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201977%20election%20was%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20for%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20forces%20of%20different%20hues%20came%20together%20to%20take%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi.%20The%20Congress's%20old%20guard%2C%20Congress%20(O)%20merged%20with%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20Socialist%20Party%20and%20Lok%20Dal%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20Janata%20Party%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%2C%20reducing%20the%20Congress%20score%20by%20a%20whopping%20198%20seats.%20What's%20more%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20defeated%20in%20Raebareli%20by%20Raj%20Narain%20-%20the%20only%20time%20a%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20lost%20an%20election.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20election%2C%20Janata%20Party%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20Morarji%20Desai%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Legacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Party's%20government%20could%20not%20complete%20its%20full%20term%20due%20to%20differences%20among%20the%20many%20forces%20under%20its%20canopy.%20Its%20split%20in%201979%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20return%20triumphant%20return%20in%20the%201980%20elections.%20But%20the%20resistance%20had%20achieved%20its%20objective.%20The%20illusion%20of%20invincibility%20had%20been%20shattered.%20Fifty%20years%20on%2C%20Emergency%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20key%20subject%20in%20the%20barbs%20exchanged%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20Congress.%20While%20the%20BJP%20mocks%20Congress's%20'save%20the%20Consti