e%20Om%20Birla%20for%20the%20post%20again.%20BJP's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fom-birla-5-points-about-new-lok-sabha-speaker-a-3-time-bjp-mp-from-rajasthans-kota-5964630%5C%22%3EOm%20Birla%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20Speaker%20in%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Sources%20said%20that%20Mr%20Birla%20will%20file%20his%20nomination%20at%2011.30%20am%20today.%20%3Cstrong%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-live-updates-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-bjp-congress-pm-modi-parliament-live-updates-remaining-281-lok-sabha-mps-to-take-oath-today-5963960%5C%22%3ELive%20Updates%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20fielded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-suresh-files-nomination-for-speakers-post-forcing-election-for-first-time-5964743%5C%22%3EK%20Suresh%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Mr%20Birla%2C%20the%20first%20time%20in%20decades%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20for%20the%20key%20post.%20A%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20is%20elected%20by%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20MPs%20voting%20and%20all%20speakers%20until%20now%20had%20been%20elected%20with%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20thanks%20to%20brute%20majorities%20after%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%2C%20was%20unchallenged%20in%20nominating%20Sumitra%20Mahajan%20and%20Om%20Birla%20to%20the%20post.%20This%20time%2C%20though%2C%20it%20doesn't%20quite%20have%20the%20numbers%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party%20is%20the%20single-largest%20in%20Parliament%20with%20240%20seats%20but%20is%2032%20short%20of%20a%20majority%2C%20meaning%20it%20relies%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20had%20said%20that%20they%20would%20back%20the%20NDA's%20choice%20of%20speaker%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20deputy%20speaker's%20post.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20that%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20should%20be%20from%20the%20Opposition%20benches.%20The%20Congress%20chief%20has%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Oppositions%20wants%20consensus%20too%2C%20healthy%20traditions%20must%20be%20followed%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20held%20talks%20with%20PM%20Modi%20ahead%20of%20day%202%20of%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOm%20Birla%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%20since%20his%20early%20days%20as%20a%20student%20leader.%20He%20currently%20serves%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Kota-Bundi%20constituency%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20was%20reelected%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Previously%2C%20he%20served%20three%20terms%20as%20a%20legislator%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Birla%20was%20unanimously%20elected%20as%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20MP%20from%20Rajasthan%20to%20hold%20the%20position.%20His%20selection%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20surprise%20by%20many%2C%20but%20he%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20his%20ability%20to%20take%20everyone%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla's%20opponent%20K%20Suresh%20secured%20his%20eighth%20consecutive%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Mavelikkara.%20He%20defeated%20CPI's%20emerging%20leader%20CA%20Arun%20Kumar%20by%20a%20narrow%20margin%20of%2010%2C000%20votes%2C%20one%20of%20the%20smallest%20in%20the%20state.%20Mavelikkara%20is%20a%20constituency%20where%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20(LDF)%20dominates%20all%20seven%20Assembly%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20a%20top%20contender%20for%20the%20Kerala%20Congress%20chief%20position%20in%202021%2C%20Mr%20Suresh%20is%20currently%20a%20special%20invitee%20to%20the%20Congr