%20some%20of%20the%20activities%20of%20Chinese%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20curtail%20and%20to%20limit%20certain%20kinds%20of%20access%2C%20and%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20generally%2C%20particularly%20in%20technological%20programs%20across%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257d14d2c-30b3-4ece-9b47-7abf82293431%5C%22%3EChinese%20academics%20have%20already%20faced%20Trump-era%20restrictions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20Trump%20era%2C%20there%20were%20policies%20in%20place%20to%20restrict%20Chinese%20access%20to%20developments%20in%20the%20US%20academic%20space%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fstuartanderson%2F2021%2F08%2F10%2Fbiden-keeps-costly-trump-visa-policy-denying-chinese-grad-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenying%20visas%20to%20Chinese%20graduate%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20the%20Chinese%20universities%20they%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20also%20enacted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustice-department-china-initiative-trump-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20Initiative%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20program%20aimed%20at%20countering%20China's%20economic%20espionage%20and%20preventing%20trade%20secret%20theft.%20The%20China%20Initiative%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustice-department-china-initiative-trump-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrapped%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20after%20critics%20said%20it%20promoted%20an%20anti-Asian%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20now%2C%20Chinese%20students%20say%20that%20they%20have%20been%20facing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F03%2F14%2Fchina-united-states-university-students-border%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%