cting%20on%20this%20period%2C%20continues%20to%20remind%20the%20nation%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20spot%26quot%3B%20inflicted%20on%20democracy%20by%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20oath%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20vowed%20to%20prevent%20such%20%26quot%3Bdark%20days%20of%20Emergency%26quot%3B%20from%20ever%20happening%20again.%20He%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20safeguard%20democracy%20from%20any%20form%20of%20oppression%2C%20Modi%20Archives%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20Emergency%20did%20not%20start%20on%20June%2025%2C%201975.%20It%20was%20preceded%20by%20widespread%20student-led%20agitations%20against%20Congress'%20corruption%2C%20with%20Gujarat%20being%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%201974%20Navnirman%20Andolan%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20PM%20Modi%20witnessed%20the%20power%20of%20student%20voices%20in%20driving%20change.%20As%20a%20Yuva%20Pracharak%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20he%20was%20deputed%20to%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20where%20he%20passionately%20supported%20the%20youth%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20Emergency%20was%20imposed%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20actively%20joined%20the%20protests.%20Despite%20peak%20censorship%2C%20he%20and%20other%20volunteers%20organised%20meetings%20and%20disseminated%20underground%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollaborating%20with%20senior%20RSS%20leaders%20like%20Nath%20Zagda%20and%20Vasant%20Gajendragadkar%2C%20he%20found%20innovative%20ways%20to%20spread%20information.%20He%20loaded%20materials%20related%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Congress%20government's%20excesses%20onto%20trains%20departing%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20ensuring%20messages%20reached%20remote%20places%20with%20less%20risk%20of%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20RSS%20going%20underground%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20Lok%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20was%20established.%20At%20just%2025%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20quickly%20rose%20to%20become%20the%20RSS%20General%20Secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20articles%20and%20correspondence%20were%20crucial%20in%20sustaining%20the%20revolt%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20even%20as%20key%20movement%20leaders%20were%20arrested%20under%20the%20MISA%20Act.%20Narendra%20Modi%20also%20reached%20out%20internationally%2C%20sending%20underground%20publications%20to%20amplify%20global%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi's%20colleagues%20abroad%20sent%20photocopies%20of%20newspapers%20that%20featured%20anti-Emergency%20articles.%20He%20ensured%20these%20copies%20were%20delivered%20to%20jails.%20To%20avoid%20detection%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20adopted%20various%20disguises%2C%20sometimes%20as%20a%20Swamiji%20or%20a%20Sikh%2C%20effectively%20evading%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Emergency%20was%20lifted%20in%201977%2C%20Narendra%20Modi's%20activism%20gained%20national%20recognition.%20He%20was%20appointed%20'Sambhag%20Pracharak'%20of%20South%20and%20Central%20Gujarat%2C%20preparing%20official%20RSS%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201978%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2027%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20authored%20his%20first%20book%2C%20'Sangharsh%20Ma%20Gujarat'%2C%20chronicling%20his%20experiences%20and%20the%20collective%20resistance%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20The%20book%2C%20launched%20by%20then-Chief%20Minister%20Babubhai%20Jasbhai%20Patel%2C%20received%20praise%20for%20its%20comprehensive%20and%20objective%20approach.%20Patel%20himself%20acknowledged%20the%20book's%20%26quot%3Bwealth%20of%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20this%20period%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20described%20the%20Emergency%20as%20%26quot%3Baapda%20mein%20avsar%26quot%3B%20(opportunity%20in%20difficult%20times)%2C%20which%20allowed%20him%20to%20collaborate%20with%20diverse%20leaders%20and%20ideologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20consensus%20in%20governance%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20majority%20is%20required%20to%20run%20the%20government%2C%20but%20to%20run%20the%20country%2C%20consensus%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719303840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fj0ev61k_narendra-modi-during-emergency-in-1975_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-pm-narendra-modi-as-rss-yuva-pracharak-resisted-emergency-50-years-ago-5965272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22June%2025%20marks%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20a%20dark%20chapter%20in%20India's%20democratic%20history.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20reflecting%20on%20this%20period%2C%20continues%20to%20remind%20the%20nation%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20spot%26quot%3B%20inflicted%20on%20democracy%20by%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-pm-narendra-modi-as-rss-yuva-pracharak-resisted-emergency-50-years-ago-5965272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-pm-narendra-modi-as-rss-yuva-pracharak-resisted-emergency-50-years-ago-5965272%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-pm-narendra-modi-as-rss-yuva-pracharak-resisted-emergency-50-years-ago-5965272%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Attacks%20on%20Jews%20and%20Muslims%20in%20Germany%20surged%20after%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20outbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719303660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F06%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-kreuzberg-germany_6590384.jpg%3F20240625111804%22%2C%22originID%2