fe%20and%20chloroform.%C2%A0Plumb%20also%20allegedly%20confided%20in%20a%20man%20known%20as%20Marc%20online%2C%20an%20undercover%20police%20officer%20based%20in%20the%20US.%20A%20video%20sent%20to%20him%20by%20Plumb%C2%A0showed%20a%20%26quot%3Bkit%20of%20sexualised%20paraphernalia%26quot%3B%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20bed%2C%20including%20hand%20and%20ankle%20shackles%2C%20a%20rope%20and%20a%20ball%20gag.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20had%20carefully%20planned%20how%20to%20kidnap%20her%20from%20her%20home%2C%20take%20her%20to%20his%20residence%20in%20Harlow%2C%20Essex%2C%20and%20murder%20her%20in%20an%20abandoned%20building%20where%20her%20screams%20''can't%20be%20heard.''%20According%20to%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjun%2F24%2Fus-police-officer-blocked-mans-plan-to-abduct-and-kill-holly-willoughby-court-told%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Plumb%20had%20amassed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20images%20of%20Ms%20Willoughby%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20which%20included%20deepfake%20pornography.%C2%A0He%20also%20tracked%20her%20movements%20and%20activities%20using%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20Plumb%20posted%20in%20an%20online%20group%20called%20'Abduct%20Lovers'.%20He%20wrote%2C%20''Getting%20this%20b*tch%20is%20all%20I%20can%20think%20about.%20I%20have%20wanted%20this%20for%20years.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20living%20out%20my%20ultimate%20fantasy.''%20The%20next%20month%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20''Getting%20her%20has%20been%20my%20ultimate%20fantasy%20for%20way%20too%20long.%20I'm%20now%20at%20the%20point%20where%20fantasy%20isn't%20enough%20anymore.%20I%20want%20the%20real%20thing.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Plumb%20was%20arrested%20in%20October%202023%20when%20the%20undercover%20US%20police%20officer%20thwarted%20his%20sinister%20plans%20and%20alerted%20the%20Met%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20was%20not%20just%20the%20ramblings%20of%20a%20fantasist.%20The%20defendant%20had%20carefully%20planned%20what%20he%20would%20do%20and%20how%20he%20would%20do%20it%2C%20purchasing%20items%20that%20would%20assist%20him%20in%20carrying%20out%20the%20attack%2C''%20prosecutor%20Alison%20Morgan%20KC%20told%20the%20trial%20at%20Chelmsford%20Crown%20Court%20on%20Monday.%20He%20further%20said%20Plumb's%20plans%20%26quot%3Bwould%20have%20involved%20catastrophic%20violence%20against%20her%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20were%20not%20disrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Plumb%20had%20already%20been%20convicted%20twice%20for%20crimes%20related%20to%20kidnapping.%20In%202006%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20force%20two%20women%20off%20a%20train%20with%20a%20fake%20gun%20and%20a%20threatening%20note.%20Two%20years%20earlier%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20tie%20up%20two%20teenage%20girls%20in%20a%20Woolworths%20stock%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ms%20Willoughby%20has%20waived%20her%20right%20to%20anonymity%20in%20the%20case.%20She%20hosted%20%3Cem%3E'This%20Morning'%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%2014%20years%20before%20stepping%20down%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20model%20before%20starting%20her%20stint%20in%20television.%20In%20August%202007%2C%20she%20married%20Dan%20Baldwin%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Hungry%20Bear%20Media.%20They%20live%20in%20Barnes%2C%20London%20and%20have%20two%20sons%20and%20a%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%2C%20expected%20to%20last%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20continues.%C2%A0Plumb%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20charges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719300960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fkuvq9eeg_holly-willoughby_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsecurity-guard-obsessed-with-uk-tv-presenter-holly-willoughby-plotted-to-kidnap-rape-and-murder-her-5964837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20had%20carefully%20planned%20how%20to%20abduct%20her%20fr