re%20scientists%20from%20around%20the%20world%20conduct%20experiments%20in%20microgravity%20conditions%2C%20invaluable%20for%20advancements%20in%20biology%2C%20physics%2C%20astronomy%2C%20and%20materials%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECostly%20Endeavor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConstructing%20and%20maintaining%20the%20ISS%20has%20been%20a%20monumental%20financial%20effort%2C%20surpassing%20%24150%20billion%20since%20its%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperational%20Dynamics%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECircling%20the%20Earth%20at%20an%20astounding%20speed%20of%2028%2C165.00%20kilometers%20per%20hour%2C%20the%20ISS%20completes%2016%20orbits%20daily%2C%20providing%20astronauts%20aboard%20with%2016%20sunrises%20and%20sunsets%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20Collaboration%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20partnership%20involving%20five%20space%20agencies%20from%2015%20countries%20manages%20the%20ISS%2C%20although%20India%20remains%20outside%20this%20consortium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20Presence%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20November%202000%2C%20the%20ISS%20has%20continuously%20housed%20astronauts%2C%20offering%20a%20living%20and%20working%20environment%20larger%20than%20a%20typical%20six-bedroom%20house.%20It%20includes%20amenities%20like%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20a%20gymnasium%2C%20and%20a%20panoramic%20bay%20window%20for%20a%20breathtaking%20360-degree%20view%20of%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustainable%20Living%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20ensure%20self-sufficiency%2C%20the%20ISS%20employs%20advanced%20recycling%20systems%20that%20purify%20sweat%20and%20urine%20into%20potable%20water%2C%20a%20crucial%20innovation%20for%20prolonged%20space%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicrobial%20Evolution%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Despite%20its%20sterile%20appearance%2C%20the%20closed%20environment%20of%20the%20ISS%20fosters%20the%20development%20of%20resilient%20microorganisms%20dubbed%20'super%20bugs%2C'%20posing%20unique%20challenges%20for%20crew%20health%20and%20station%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisible%20Wonder%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20it%20orbits%20overhead%2C%20the%20ISS%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%20from%20Earth.%20Enthusiasts%20can%20track%20its%20path%20through%20the%20night%20sky%20using%20resources%20provided%20by%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20Prospects%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20no%20Indian%20has%20yet%20visited%20the%20ISS%2C%20plans%20are%20underway%20for%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20mission%20there%20soon.%20India%20also%20aims%20to%20establish%20its%20own%20space%20station%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station%2C%20by%202040%2C%20reflecting%20a%20growing%20ambition%20in%20space%20exploration.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719299820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbp8pog74_international-space-station-getty_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-unique-mini-city-in-space-the-international-space-station-5964898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20of%20human%20engineering%20and%20international%20collaboration%2C%20has%20been%20orbiting%20Earth%20for%2025%20years.%20Here%20are%20ten%20fascinating%20facts%20about%20this%20cosmic%20outpost%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-unique-mini-city-in-space-the-international-space-station-5964898%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-unique-mini-city-in-space-the-international-space-station-5964898%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-unique-mini-city-in-space-the-international-space-station-5964898%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pashtun%20Tahafuz%20Movement%20holds%20massive%20rally%20to%20prot