Fa%3EDr.%20Joseph%20Antoun's%20approach%20to%20fitness%20is%20relatively%20simple%20and%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20age%2C%20muscles%20become%20%26quot%3Ban%20organ%20of%20longevity%2C%26quot%3B%20Antoun%20said.%20Once%20you%20hit%2040%2C%20you%20naturally%20start%20to%20lose%20muscle%2C%20which%20slows%20down%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-exercise-doesnt-help-you-lose-weight-chart-fat-loss-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emetabolic%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20the%20body%20burns%20fewer%20calories%2C%20he%20said.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20weight%20gain%20and%20put%20a%20person%20at%20risk%20of%20developing%20related%20health%20conditions%20such%20as%20type%202%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarcopenia%2C%20or%20age-related%20muscle%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20function%20loss%2C%20is%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20increased%20falls%2C%20frailty%2C%20and%20fractures%20in%20older%20people%2C%20which%20can%20result%20in%20them%20losing%20their%20independence%20as%20they%20struggle%20to%20complete%20daily%20tasks%20on%20their%20own%2C%20according%20to%20Cleveland%20Clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Antoun%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20longevity-focused%20nutrition%20company%20L-Nutra%2C%20exercises%20three%20to%20four%20times%20a%20week%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-lifestyle-habits-live-longer-healthier-no-gym-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintegrates%20movement%20into%20his%20busy%20workday%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20muscle%20mass%20and%20get%20his%20heart%20rate%20up.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20so%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20he%20works%20out%20to%20stay%20healthy%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251577ebf-18ee-4f05-9cca-21b3c1c5ce33%5C%22%3EWalking%2010%2C000%20steps%20a%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntoun%20aims%20to%20walk%2010%2C000%20steps%20each%20day.%20%26quot%3BSix%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in%20LA%2C%20and%20I%20never%20bought%20a%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20walks%20to%20work%20every%20day%20and%20takes%20lots%20of%20his%20meetings%20on%20his%20AirPods%20while%20walking%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20four%20AirPods%20because%20everywhere%20I%20go%20I%20just%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20can%20walk%20and%20talk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvidence%20suggests%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalking-steps-a-day-lower-risk-dying-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalking%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%20increases%20a%20person's%20chances%20of%20living%20a%20long%2C%20healthy%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%20study%20published%20in%20the%20European%20Journal%20of%20Preventive%20Cardiology%20found%20that%20walking%204%2C000%20steps%20a%20day%20reduced%20the%20risk%20of%20dying%20early%20from%20any%20cause%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20more%20a%20person%20walked%20the%20lower%20the%20risk.%20(The%20study%20only%20looked%20at%20data%20for%20up%20to%2020%2C000%20steps).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20study%20authors%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F08%2F24%2Fwell%2Fmove%2Fcardio-strength-training-benefits.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20switching%20from%20a%20sedentary%20lifestyle%20to%20having%20a%20workout%20schedule%20was%20comparable%20to%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20versus%20not%20smoking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295642595-c3ce-4c20-9c2e-35e5f2478594%5C%22%3ECardio%20and%20strength%20training%203%20to%204%20times%20a%20week%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntoun%20works%20out%20three%20or%20four%20times%20a%20week%2C%20doing%20a%20mixture%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-better-cardio-burning-fat-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%20and%20cardio%3C