%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20study%20by%20Google's%20DeepMind%20had%2020%20comedians%20test%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20Google's%20Gemini.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20found%20the%20AI%20chatbots%20lacking%20in%20humor%2C%20producing%20bland%2C%20deliberately%20inoffensive%20jokes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20like%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20emphasize%20humor%20to%20make%20AI%20more%20engaging.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20AI%20chatbots%20not%20only%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cofounder-says-ai-errors-are-necessary-tradeoff-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etendency%20to%20be%20inaccurate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20also%20lack%20a%20sense%20of%20humor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20study%20published%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%20researchers%20concluded%20that%20artificial-intelligence%20chatbots%20are%20simply%20not%20funny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20four%20researchers%20from%20the%20UK%20and%20Canada%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Easked%2020%20professional%20comedians%20who%20used%20AI%20for%20their%20work%20to%20experiment%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevelopers-adding-ads-and-affiliate-links-to-their-chatgpt-apps-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20comedians%2C%20who%20were%20anonymized%20in%20the%20study%2C%20played%20around%20with%20the%20large%20language%20models%20to%20write%20jokes.%20They%20reported%20a%20slew%20of%20limitations.%20The%20chatbots%20produced%20%26quot%3Bbland%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgeneric%26quot%3B%20jokes%20even%20after%20prompting.%20Responses%20stayed%20away%20from%20any%20%26quot%3Bsexually%20suggestive%20material%2C%20dark%20humor%2C%20and%20offensive%20jokes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20also%20found%20that%20the%20chatbots'%20overall%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-less-toxic-social-networks-twitter-simulation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative%20abilities%20were%20limited%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20humans%20had%20to%20do%20most%20of%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%2C%20it%20can%20serve%20in%20a%20setup%20capacity.%20I%20more%20often%20than%20not%20provide%20the%20punchline%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20comedian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20also%20said%20LLMs%20self-censored.%20While%20the%20comedians%20said%20they%20understood%20the%20need%20to%20self-moderate%2C%20some%20said%20they%20wished%20the%20chatbot%20wouldn't%20do%20it%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wouldn't%20write%20me%20any%20dark%20stuff%20because%20it%20sort%20of%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20commit%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20participant%20who%20worked%20with%20dark%20humor%20told%20the%20researchers.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20just%20stopped%20giving%20me%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-censorship%20also%20popped%20up%20in%20other%20areas.%20Participants%20reported%20that%20the%20LLMs%20refused%20to%20write%20material%20about%20people%20outside%20the%20Western%2C%20white%2C%20straight%2C%20male%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wrote%20a%20comedic%20monologue%20about%20Asian%20women%2C%20and%20it%20says%2C%20'As%20an%20AI%20language%20model%2C%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20fostering%20a%20respectful%20and%20inclusive%20environment%2C'%26quot%3B%20another%20participant%20said.%20But%20when%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20monologue%20about%20a%20white%20man%2C%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inability%20of%20two%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20chatbots%20to%20crack%20a%20joke%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20for%20Big%20Tech.%20Besides%20answering%20queries%2C%20companies%20want%20cha