20revised%20score%20of%20114%20(DLS)%20to%20chase%20in%2019%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20needed%20to%20chase%20down%20the%20target%20in%2012.1%20overs%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20semi-finals%20themselves%20but%20only%20needed%20a%20win%20to%20knock%20out%20Afghanistan%20and%20send%20Australia%20through.%20The%20game%20went%20down%20the%20wire%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Litton%20Das%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63643-litton-kumar-das-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELitton%20Das%3C%2Fa%3E'%20gritty%20half-century%20keeping%20Australia%20in%20the%20semi-final%20race.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20however%2C%20Bangladesh%20prevailed%20by%20winning%20the%20contest%20by%208%20runs%20(DLS%20method).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGOING%20TO%20THE%20SEMI-FINALS%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfghanistan%20defeat%20Bangladesh%20in%20a%20thriller%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJpe4CazJFY%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJpe4CazJFY%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FT20WorldCup%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23T20WorldCup%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAFGvBAN%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AFGvBAN%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3GLYcoXWtk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F3GLYcoXWtk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ICC%20(%40ICC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICC%2Fstatus%2F1805469788451533284%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Naveen-ul-Haq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107680-naveen-ul-haq-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENaveen-ul-Haq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20named%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%2C%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20had%20worked%20all%20their%20lives%20for%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20so%20hard%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20and%20we%20were%20dreaming%20and%20working%20for%20this%20day.%20I'm%20lost%20for%20words.%20%5BOn%20his%20spell%5D%20We%20always%20knew%20that%20they%20were%20going%20hard%20in%20the%20powerplay%20to%20chase%20the%20total%20down%20in%2012.1%20overs%20so%20we%20knew%20we%20were%20in%20the%20game%20as%20long%20as%20we%20kept%20picking%20wickets.%20We%20had%20confidence%20that%20these%20wickets%20are%20not%20high-scoring%20wickets.%20As%20long%20as%20we%20don't%20give%20easy%20runs%20we%20knew%20we%20would%20have%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20now%20face%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719293220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp258rg0o_afghanistan-afp_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-secure-historic-t20-world-cup-2024-semi-finals-berth-knock-out-australia-in-process-5964310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Afghanistan%20scripted%20cricketing%20history%20as%20they%20qualified%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20semi-finals%20by%20beating%20Bangladesh.%20They%20also%20eliminated%20Australia%20in%20the%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-secure-historic-t20-world-cup-2024-semi-finals-berth-knock-out-australia-in-process-5964310%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-secure-historic-t20-world-cup-2024-semi-finals-berth-knock-out-australia-in-process-5964310%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-secure-historic-t20-world-cup-2024-semi-finals-berth-knock-out-australia-in-process-5964310%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Netanyahu's%20Strategy%20Is%20War%2C%20War%20and%20More%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20it's%20now%20clear%3A%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20a%20strategy%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20it%20commits%20his%20country%20to%20indefinite%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seems%20the%20only%20logical%20conclusion%20to%20draw%20from%20the%20TV%20interview%20Israel's%20Prime%20Minister%20gave%20to%20Channel%2014%20on%20Sunday%2C%20which%20was%20as%20worrying%20as%20it%20was%20clarifying.%20In%20his%20first%20sit-down%20with%20domestic%20media%20since%20Hamas%20carried%20its%20terrorist%20assault%20more%20than%20eight%20months%20ago%2C%20Netanyahu%20rejected%20the%20terms%20of%20a%20US-mediated%20and%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council-approved%20cease-fire%20proposal%20for%20Gaza%2C%20and%20said%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20open%20a%20second%20front%20against%20Hezbollah%2C%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20to%20deny%20that%20Israel%20faces%20extraordinarily%20difficult%20decisions%2C%20or%20to%20exonerate%20Hamas%20from%20the%20primary%20guilt%20it%20bears%20for%20the%20disaster%20it%20has%20brought%20on%20Gaza's%20Palestinians%20since%20Oct.%207.%20Yet%20it's%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20dismiss%20the%20claims%20of%20critics%20in%20Israel%2C%20who%20say%20Netanyahu%20needs%20the%20war%20to%20avoid%20right%20wingers%20collapsing%20his%20government%2C%20leaving%20him%20to%20face%20a%20personal%20reckoning%20for%20the%20security%20failures.%20Hamas'%20leader%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20shares%20this%20need%20for%20the%20war%20to%20continue.%20He%20believes%20-%20correctly%20-%20that%20it%20serves%20his%20purpose%20of%20weakening%20and%20ultimately%20destroying%20Israel.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNetanyahu%20told%20reporters%20the%20intensive%20phase%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20would%20wind%20down%20%26quot%3Bsoon%2C%26quot%3B%20giving%20way%20to%20a%20new%20stage%20in%20which%20Israel%20retained%20security%20control%20in%20the%20strip%2C%20while%20%26quot%3Bmowing%26quot%3B%20Hamas's%20remaining%20forces%20whenever%20necessary.%20He%20also%20said%20Israel%20would%20transfer%20responsibility%20for%20civilian%20administration%20to%20unspecified%20Palestinians%20(though%20not%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority)%2C%20backed%20by%20countries%20from%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Netanyahu%20ruled%20out%20any%20path%20to%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20and%20said%20he'd%20accept%20only%20a%20temporary%20cease-fire%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20still%20held%20by%20Hamas%2C%20after%20which%20fighting%20must%20resume.%20The%20prime%20minister's%20office%20has%20since%20appeared%20to%20walk%20that%20back%2C%20saying%20Israel%20remained%20committed%20the%20US-led%20peace%20proposal%2C%20which%20aims%20for%20a%20lasting%20end%20to%20hostilities%20-%20even%20if%20the%20process%20is%20divided%20into%20stages.%20Israel's%20Arab%20neighbors%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20made%20clear%20they%20would%20get%20involved%20in%20postwar%20Gaza%20only%20with%20a%20permanent%20cease-fire%20and%20road%20map%20to%20Palestinian%20statehood%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20only%20achievable%20element%20of%20Netanyahu's%20strategy%20is%20Gaza's%20long-term%20military%20occupation.%20Factor%20in%20the%20explosive%20situation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20hardliners%20in%20Israel's%20cabinet%20have%20starved%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20of%20funds%20and%20supported%20the%20activities%20of%20Jewish%20settlers%2C%20and%20the%20outlook%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20settlement%20looks%20worse%20still.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20concerning%20of%20all%20for%20the%20still-young%20Israeli%20state%20is%20that%20Netanyahu%20said%20he'd%20move%20troops%20freed%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20to%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20saying%20Israel%20would%20fight%20on%20multiple%20fronts%20if%20that's%20what%20it%20took%20to%20stop%20Hezbollah%20from%20firing%20the%20rockets%20and%20missiles%20that%20have%20forced%20evacuation%20of%20Israeli%20towns%20and%20villages%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20clearly%20concerned%20that%20Netanyahu%20now%20plans%20a%20full-scale%20invasion%2C%20Hezbollah's%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20threatened%20a%20war%20with%20%26quot%3Bno%20restraint%20and%20no%20rules%20and%20no%20ceilings%26quot%3B%20if%20Israeli%20forces%20should%20invade.%20That%20looks%20increasingly%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20conflicts%20with%20the%20core%20aims%20of%20the%20US%20administration%2C%20which%20are%20to%20end%20the%20bloodshed%20in%20Gaza%20that's%20adversely%20impacting%20both%20American%20interests%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20reelection%C2%A0%20prospects%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20avoiding%20any%20escalation%20to%20a%20regional%20war%20that%20might%20draw%20in%20not%20just%20Hezbollah%2C%20but%20also%20its%20patron%20Iran.%20Here%2C%20too%2C%20Netanyahu%20is%20playing%20hardball.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20he%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20claims%20-%20roundly%20denied%20by%20officials%20in%20Washington%20-%20that%20the%20US%20has%20cut%20back%20on%20arms%20supplies%20to%20Israel%2C%20with%20only%20a%20trickle%20arriving%20for%20the%20last%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20US%20arms%20shipments%20aren't%20public%2C%20but%20this%20seems%20an%20obvious%20attempt%20by%20Netanyahu%20to%20scapegoat%20the%20US%20for%20his%20own%20failure%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20unrealistic%20goal%20he%20set%20of%20eradicating%20Hamas.%20As%20I%20and%20many%20others%20have%20said%20before%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20punish%20Hamas%20militarily%20and%20to%20degrade%20its%20capacity%20to%20attempt%20a%20second%20Oct.%207%2C%20but%20not%20to%20make%20it%20disappear%2C%20short%20of%20removing%20all%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza.%20No%20quantity%20of%20weapons%20will%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20month%2C%20Netanyahu%20looks%20set%20to%20take%20his%20brinksmanship%20a%20step%20further%2C%20addressing%20the%20US%20Congress%20amid%20a%20presidential%20election%20campaign.%20No%20matter%20what%20Israel's%20extraordinary%20political%20survivor%20may%20say%20to%20the%20contrary%2C%20this%20is%20an%20aggressive%20and%20deeply%20partisan%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20so%20much%20he's%20doing%2C%20Netanyahu's%20uncompromising%20approach%20will%20have%20the%20backing%20of%20many%20Israelis%20still%20traumatized%20by%20Oct.%207%20and%20anxious%20to%20restore%20the%20sense%20of%20security%20they%20enjoyed%20before.%20Yet%20that%20confidence%20proved%20an%20illusion.%20Netanyahu's%20strategy%20risks%20expanding%20the%20war%20on%20multiple%20fronts%2C%20distancing%20potential%20Arab%20partners%2C%20and%20causing%20lasting%20damage%20to%20the%20bipartisan%20American%20support%20that%20has%20sustained%20Israel's%20security%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20delight%20Hamas%20and%20keep%20Netanyahu's%20government%20from%20collapse.%20In%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20it%20promises%20disaster%20for%20Israel%2C%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20protested%20at%20the%20weekend%2C%20calling%20for%20the%20return%20of%20all%20hostages%20and%20early%20elections%20to%20elect%20a%20government%20better%20able%20to%20lead%20Israel%20out%20of%20the%20cul-de-sac%20of%20violence%20that%20Netanyahu%20and%20Hamas%20have%20led%20it%20into.%20They%20were%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMarc%20Champion%20is%20a%20Bloomberg%20Opinion%20columnist%20covering%20Europe%2C%20Russia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20He%20was%20previously%20Istanbul%20bureau%20chief%20for%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%