%3Cfigcaption%3EFootage%20shows%20a%20uniformed%20officer%20and%20two%20men%20in%20hard%20hats%20placing%20a%20villager's%20hand%20grenade%20in%20bubble%20wrap.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FWeibo%2FBaokang%20Public%20Security%20Bureau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20police%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20secured%20a%20grenade%20kept%20as%20a%20hammer%20by%20a%20villager%20in%20Hubei.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuthorities%20say%20they%20dispatched%C2%A0%26quot%3Bprofessional%20bomb%20disposal%20personnel%26quot%3B%20to%20retrieve%20the%20explosive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20video%20published%20by%20police%20showed%20two%20men%20in%20T-shirts%20and%20hard%20hats%20putting%20the%20grenade%20in%20bubble%20wrap.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20China's%20Hubei%20province%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20had%20confiscated%20a%20hand%20grenade%20kept%20by%20a%2090-year-old%20villager%20for%2020%20years%20as%20a%20hammer%20for%20everyday%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Public%20Security%20Bureau%20of%20Baokang%20County%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F5594989852%2FOkuM20mKR%3Flayerid%3D5048848580087473%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20a%20video%20of%20the%20grenade's%20retrieval%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20said%20the%20unnamed%20female%20villager%20discovered%20it%20in%20a%20field%20decades%20ago%20and%2C%20believing%20it%20to%20be%20a%20lump%20of%20iron%2C%20had%20been%20using%20it%20to%20crack%20walnuts%2C%20hammer%20nails%2C%20and%20pound%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grenade%20was%20only%20discovered%20on%20Sunday%20when%20an%20old%20building%20belonging%20to%20the%20woman%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Huangbao%20was%20being%20demolished%2C%20according%20to%20the%20post%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20police%20deployed%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%20bomb%20disposal%20personnel%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20shows%20two%20men%20dressed%20in%20T-shirts%2C%20