major%20income%20source%20with%20plummeting%20profitability.%20It%20became%20costlier%20to%20produce%20rubber%20than%20to%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20around%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20and%20the%20selling%20price%20was%20Rs%20110%20per%20kg.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rates%20in%20rubber%20were%20dwindling%20as%20farmers%20could%20fetch%20only%20Rs%20100%20per%20kg%20from%20rubber.%20A%20labourer%20could%20earn%20more%20wages%20daily.%20It%20was%20not%20sufficient%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20reconsidered%20the%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20replace%20seven%20acres%20of%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20rubber%20trees%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295835%2Fcoconut-farmer-senior-citizen-grows-mangosteen-from-malaysia-exports-to-gulf-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20pepper%2C%20areca%20nut%2C%20coconut%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20axed%20most%20of%20the%20rubber%20trees%20to%20try%20new%20plantations.%20People%20called%20me%20a%20madman%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20progressive%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biju%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet