self.%20Ultimately%20you%20just%20have%20to%20remind%20yourself%20that%20some%20days%20are%20difficult%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine.%20Good%20sleep%20and%20good%20food%20do%20wonders%20for%20me%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinning%20the%20title%20has%20brought%20Akash%20increased%20visibility%20and%20love%20from%20all%20around.%20He%20hopes%20to%20continue%20exploring%20South%20Indian%20food%20and%20presenting%20it%20in%20new%20ways%20through%20pop-ups%20and%20by%20starting%20a%20supper%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20leave%20you%20with%20Akash%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20for%20this%20mouthwatering%20dish%20%E2%80%94%20Sapota%20Kesari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akash%20Muralidharan's%20sapota%20kesari%20masterchef%20recipe%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-6-1718939406-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353747%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Akash%20Muralidharan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718949570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2