orts%2C%20they%20made%20sure%20they%20were%20there%20at%20every%20practice%20sitting%20on%20the%20front%20row%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20days%2C%20sports%20was%20a%20passion%2C%20other%20days%2C%20it%20was%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20safe%20space.%20Her%20chubbiness%2C%20which%20had%20been%20adored%20when%20she%20was%20little%2C%20was%20ridiculed%20as%20she%20got%20older.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20can%E2%80%99t%20I%20just%20fit%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20thought%20many%20a%20time%2C%20opting%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20instead%20of%20going%20out%20since%20she%20did%20not%20want%20to%20endure%20endless%20taunts%20about%20her%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20in%20isolation%2C%20she%20struck%20an%20unusual%20%E2%80%94%20albeit%20special%20%E2%80%94%20friendship%20with%20sports.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20phase%20that%20the%20club%20Hetal%20attended%20for%20judo%20organised%20a%20sumo%20wrestling%20championship.%20The%20more%20she%20learned%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fsports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20new%20sport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20more%20she%20resonated%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20term%20people%20thin%20and%20fat.%20But%20in%20Japan%2C%20being%20the%20latter%20is%20not%20something%20bad.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20one%20is%20a%20sumo%20wrestler%20in%20Japan%2C%20they%20are%20not%20called%20%E2%80%98fat%E2%80%99%20but%20rather%2C%20%E2%80%98strong%E2%80%99.%20They%20are%20worshipped%2C%20they%20are%20celebrated%2C%20and%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20role%20models%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-11.49.34-PM-1-1718375444.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5